  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a calming gesture, and up to three willing creatures of your choice that you can see within range fall unconscious for the genjutsu's duration. The genjutsu ends on a target early if it takes damage or someone uses an action to shake or slap it awake. If a target remains unconscious for the full duration, that target gains the benefit of a short rest, and it can't be affected by this genjutsu again until it finishes a long rest.</p>",
